data.description: Charming ranch-style home nestled on a peaceful corner lot in the tranquil and established neighborhood of Grove Creek. This meticulously maintained residence welcomes you with two majestic mature trees at the entrance. Inside, discover all-new vinyl flooring and baseboards, newer interior paint, upgraded fixtures and led lighting, new kitchen cabinets, all complementing the updated stainless steel appliances. Complete with a gas range oven. Modern fixtures add a touch of elegance, while the farmhouse design exudes warmth and character. Enjoy the perfect blend of comfort and style in this serene haven. Your peaceful sanctuary awaits beneath the shade of those grand entrance trees. Welcome home to tranquility and timeless elegance.
